Revision history for Perl module App::PAIA

0.??    2013-??-??
  - improved unit tests

0.21    2013-11-07
  - fixed scopes read_items & write_items
  - improved error handling
  - added dependency on module URI
  - internal changes (logging etc.)

0.20    2013-10-31
  - better support --version and --help
  - new command 'config'
  - implement PAIA method 'change'
  - changed session file from .paia_session to paia-session.json
  - support Perl >= 5.10
  - facilitate writing unit tests

0.11    2013-10-23
  - implemented all PAIA method but 'change'

0.01    2013-10-22
  - First version released to CPAN
